        {% include '../components/nav.njk' %}
        <div id="wrap">
            {# Content minimum height wrapper, place between nav and footer #}
            <div class='hero-with-cta splash-big background-dark text-dark'>
                {# Hero banner #}
                <div class="content-full-column">
                    <h1> Streamline your systems, <span class="text-highlight-cool-dark">affordably</span>.</h1>
                    <div class="container-two-columns">
                    <div>
                        <p>Your CRM should streamline and automate your sales, not just track them.</p>
                        <p>Flexible enterprise CRM at an affordable price</p>
                        <a href="{{url_get_started}}" target="_blank"><button class="button-warm-light button-large">Get started with us</button></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <iframe class="video-hero-landing" width="560" height="315" src="{{url_video_embed}}" title="{{title_video_embed}}" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container-diagonal-slash"></div>

            <div class='landing-product-overview skeleton block-full' >
                {# Product Overview #}
                <div class="flex-container" id="flexible-tech-consulting" style=" padding-inline:20%" >
                    <div class="div-sticky">
                        <div class="text-column-h1">
                            Built for your needs
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div style=" width: 50%; padding-left: 10%">
                        <div class="">
                            <h2>Modular</h2>
                            <h5>Replace your entire system or just use Rapid to plug the holes.</h5>
                            <p>We can build projects in modular blocks, so you can see the value we provide, and pay as you go.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Secure</h2>
                            <h5>Worry-free data. Our security-first platform secures your data with the best that Microsoft has to offer.</h5>
                            <p>Hosted in the Azure cloud, get enterprise grade safety without the enterprise grade development costs.</p>
                            <p>Never have to worry about losing data with item level roll-back and full edit history as standard.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Flexible</h2>
                            <h5>Need to wait for approval or sign-off? Your custom solution will be built according to your schedule, not ours.</h5>
                            <p>Our team aren’t called Rapid for nothing. With agile cycles and a focus on immediacy of result, avoid getting trapped in dead ends.</p>
                            <p>How can we build so fast? Check out our <u>Technology</u>.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Responsible</h2>
                            <h5>Technology impacts lives and we’re all in this together.</h5>
                            <p>We empower organisations through technology, but never lose sight of the human element.</p>
                            <p>We support NFPs, like <u>Simpli,</u> and are committed to supporting people trying to improve the world.</p>
                            <div class="spacer-small"></div>
                            <h2>Aussie</h2>
                            <h5>Proudly Australian owned &amp; operated, delivering excellence nationwide.</h5>
                            <p>Being an Aussie company means we understand the unique needs and values of the Australian market.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class='landing-purpose skeleton block-half background-dark'>
                {# Why we exist #}
                <div class='content-full-column text-dark'>
                    <p>We exist to make technology <strong>affordable and accessible</strong>, to drive growth and efficiency in organisations.</p>
                    <p>We exist to help organisations provide <strong>best in class experience for their customers</strong> from their first interaction to their last.</p>
                    <p>We exist to <strong>reduce the cost and complexity</strong> of enterprise CRM systems and technology so that customers can <strong>focus on making their business</strong> great rather than fighting their systems.</p>
                    <p>We exist to make cutting edge technology <strong>more accessible and effective</strong> for mid market organisations.</p>
                    <p>We exist to help organisations who have <strong>outgrown their current systems</strong> but don’t want the complexity and cost of existing enterprise solutions.</p>
                    <h4 class="text-center text-highlight-cool-dark"><u>We exist to make your life easier.</u></h4>
                </div>
            </div>

